We are submitting a manuscript entitled \'93Quantifying Limits to Detection of Early Warning for Critical Transitions\'94 by Carl Boettiger and Alan Hastings for consideration for publication in Ecology Letters.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\aspalpha\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\hich\af4\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\lang1081\cf0\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\rtlch \ltrch
